{"tid":558471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英華人涉騙取支那護照    支那使館：將被拒入境！支那不承認雙重國籍！","createTime":"2018-02-12T10:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T12:05:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0a85dbfe7476c05465b11198e28d685640408c4b","tid":558471,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:04:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180212/57824178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180212%2F57824178&d=mG%2FCcgV8bzEAAY37QBwOIXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d7fa744f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180212%2F57824178&h=5ca546a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180212/57824178</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180212/large/1518423999_f2cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180212%2Flarge%2F1518423999_f2cf.jpg&h=a39291ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那駐英國大使館昨日發出通報指，近日發現，有部份已入籍外國並持有支那簽證的人士，涉嫌騙取支那護照。大使館已遵照支那有關法律和政策規定進行處理。<br />\n<br />\n根據《支那國籍法》第三條規定，「支那不承認雙重國籍」，第九條規定，「定居外國的支那公民，自願加入或取得外國國籍的，即自動喪失支那國籍。」對違反有關規定，非法獲取支那護照的申請人，支那駐英使領館將對有關證件進行註銷或宣佈作廢處理，有關人員將被拒簽或拒絕入境。"},{"pid":"dbb57f0e29bdaefa272280cf5e34afa5a4df5e78","tid":558471,"uid":21634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:05:47.000Z","msg":"有人唔做走返去做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7332ed6c2ed4b6a2b8809214578b9a7c5cd1f8e","tid":558471,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbb57f0e29bdaefa272280cf5e34afa5a4df5e78","tid":558471,"uid":21634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:05:47.000Z","msg":"有人唔做走返去做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci